      skos:broader narr:IdiolectPhrasing ;
      skos:note "Scarlet's idiolect favors multi-clause conversational descriptions over compressed coinages. The phrase 'it speaks to, references, and works from what was already said' is characteristic: three-verb enumeration, no nominalization, no slogan cadence. This is the positive exemplar of her preferred register." ;
      rdf:value true ;
